#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:15
#: aa464f83ff4d4c12affd3b9c68084f43
msgid "MAC OS上如何查询串口号？"
msgstr "How do I check the serial port number on macOS?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:16
#: 2a38f503489e4a0d8705afc96460b3f9
msgid "通过指令“ls /dev/cu.*”查询。"
msgstr "Use the command \"ls /dev/cu.*\" to query it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:19
#: e5a312ae949542d5baf2c9a83a5e7076
msgid "CH340以及CP2102驱动获取链接："
msgstr "Download links for CH340 and CP2102 drivers:"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:20
#: c9305b950f3c49ab85081b243c8b7ff9
msgid "https://docs.ai-thinker.com/%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B72"
msgstr "https://docs.ai-thinker.com/%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B72"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:23
#: 453ceaa2940c47779b8438e0e1ab4436
msgid "你们USB转TTL（cp2102芯片）不支持2M速率么？"
msgstr "Does your USB-to-TTL adapter (CP2102 chip) not support a 2M baud rate?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:24
#: 035a3c3517724a54a8c09c796da0c899
msgid "该工具最大支持1M速率"
msgstr "This tool supports a maximum baud rate of 1M."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:27
#: 683e5293431d4410900d7c0854c44463
msgid "请问CP2102模块与CH340模块是否兼容？"
msgstr "Are the CP2102 module and CH340 module compatible?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:28
#: d52b5b4f136c4ee58cc2de68d4493aaa
msgid "均是串口模块，使用方法一样，只是驱动不同；"
msgstr ""
"Both are serial port modules and are used in the same way; only the drivers "
"are different."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:31
#: 553879a0e4eb4253a65ba8800687722e
msgid "有SDIO接口的数据透传模组么？"
msgstr ""
"Do you have a data transparent transmission module with an SDIO interface?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:32
#: ffb86852b4e646428669e873da2fe2ec
msgid "没有"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:35
#: 031b3fc094e5431ba972c2364860246d
msgid "有支持研发电台的模块吗"
msgstr "Do you have modules that support radio transceiver development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:36
#: bf4bd22d0b994cbfb2b0204bccfe1de5
msgid "目前没有支持研发电台的模组"
msgstr ""
"Currently, there are no modules that support radio transceiver development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:39
#: fa1261f5a3574b83857fd6b10368885d
msgid "请问：AiThinkerIDE_V1.5.2软件为什么老是安装失败？"
msgstr "Why does the AiThinkerIDE_V1.5.2 software keep failing to install?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:40
#: 66104048c5fa4e9d8d90ddecfbf80ad6
msgid ""
"建议换一个开发环境，该软件已经不再维护了。这是开发环境搭建指导文档： `参考链"
"接  <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/get-"
"started/windows-setup.html>`__"
msgstr ""
"It is recommended to switch to another development environment, as this "
"software is no longer maintained. Here is the development environment setup "
"guide: `Reference link  <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-"
"sdk/en/latest/get-started/windows-setup.html>`__"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:44
#: 421fcc5520a34f01969dc4d5791cbfeb
msgid "请问设备是铝合金和铁制外壳，会影响信号传输么？"
msgstr ""
"If the device has an aluminum alloy or iron enclosure, will it affect signal "
"transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:45
#: 923c2f0afaee47418ec6da7e0291762f
msgid "会，金属物质会吸收射频波，对信号传输影响很大；"
msgstr ""
"Yes. Metal materials absorb RF waves and have a significant impact on signal "
"transmission."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:48
#: 60d3b3d99f2c45efb23960e35ed902e9
msgid "CP2102串口板外面的塑料皮套有什么作用，给剪开有影响吗"
msgstr ""
"What is the purpose of the plastic sleeve outside the CP2102 serial port "
"board? Will cutting it open have any impact?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:49
#: ad5f1447a0a24e93a72c3ec96eb79593
msgid ""
"塑料皮套起到保护内部电路的作用，不推荐将皮套剪掉，这样会降低串口板的使用寿命"
msgstr ""
"The plastic sleeve protects the internal circuit. It is not recommended to "
"cut it off, as doing so will reduce the service life of the serial port "
"board."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:52
#: 564dbe4c3be54973abcad46b0adc5822
msgid "请问贵司有能驱动720P摄像头的产品么？"
msgstr "Does your company have any products that can drive a 720P camera?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/TOOL/index.rst:53
#: 0662d7b783bc4e9580b6f2f2a7e10241
msgid "没有。"
msgstr "No."
